---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="La Grange — Moulin à Rêves" description="La Grange: a converted stone barn at Moulin à Rêves. 3 bedrooms, sleeps 6, with soaring ceilings, an open kitchen, and doors onto the garden.">

  <Fragment slot="schema">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "VacationRental",
      "name": "La Grange — Moulin à Rêves",
      "description": "A converted stone barn at Moulin à Rêves. 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, sleeps 6. Soaring ceilings, an open kitchen, and doors onto the garden.",
      "url": "https://moulin-a-reves.com/homes/la-grange/",
      "image": "/images/homes/la-grange-hero.webp",
      "numberOfBedrooms": 3,
      "numberOfBathroomsTotal": 2,
      "occupancy": { "@type": "QuantitativeValue", "value": 6 },
      "floorSize": { "@type": "QuantitativeValue", "value": 140, "unitCode": "MTK" },
      "petsAllowed": true,
      "address": {
        "@type": "PostalAddress",
        "addressLocality": "Barbizon",
        "addressRegion": "Seine-et-Marne",
        "addressCountry": "FR"
      },
      "geo": {
        "@type": "GeoCoordinates",
        "latitude": 48.4433,
        "longitude": 2.6033
      },
      "amenityFeature": [
        {"@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "WiFi", "value": true},
        {"@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "Kitchen", "value": true},
        {"@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "Wood-burning Stove", "value": true},
        {"@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "Garden", "value": true},
        {"@type": "LocationFeatureSpecification", "name": "Hot Tub", "value": true}
      ]
    })} />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero__image">
      <img src="/images/homes/la-grange-hero.webp" alt="La Grange — converted stone barn with tall windows and garden views" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero__content">
      <h1 class="hero__title">La Grange</h1>
      <p class="hero__tagline" data-i18n="grange.hero.tagline">The converted barn. High ceilings, open spaces, garden at your feet.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Bar -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 48px; padding-bottom: 48px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stats-bar__item">
          <div class="stats-bar__number">3</div>
          <div class="stats-bar__label" data-i18n="grange.stats.bedrooms">Bedrooms</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-bar__item">
          <div class="stats-bar__number">2</div>
          <div class="stats-bar__label" data-i18n="grange.stats.bathrooms">Bathrooms</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-bar__item">
          <div class="stats-bar__number">6</div>
          <div class="stats-bar__label" data-i18n="grange.stats.guests">Guests</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-bar__item">
          <div class="stats-bar__number">140</div>
          <div class="stats-bar__label">m&sup2;</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Narrative Description -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container--narrow fade-in">
      <h2 data-i18n="grange.narrative.heading">The Barn, Reimagined</h2>
      <div style="margin-top: 32px;">
        <p data-i18n="grange.narrative.p1">
          You'll notice the ceiling first. When the barn door opens and you step inside La Grange for the first time, your eye goes up — past the original stone walls, past the iron tie-rods that have held the structure together for two centuries, all the way to the ridge beam five metres above. The space is honest and unhurried, the kind of volume that makes you breathe more slowly.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n="grange.narrative.p2" style="margin-top: 20px;">
          The ground floor is one generous room where cooking, eating, and living happen together. The kitchen runs along the south wall: a long oak counter, a six-burner range, and open shelving stocked with the kind of dishes you actually want to use — hand-thrown stoneware from a ceramicist in Moret-sur-Loing. The dining table is reclaimed elm, long enough for ten, positioned where the afternoon light crosses the room. You'll set it once, then leave it set for the rest of the week.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n="grange.narrative.p3" style="margin-top: 20px;">
          Double doors on the garden side fold open entirely, and the line between indoors and out disappears. The garden is not formal — it's herbs and wildflowers and an old pear tree that drops fruit in September. Breakfast here is bare feet on warm stone, coffee going cold because you got distracted watching a pair of jays argue in the hedge.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n="grange.narrative.p4" style="margin-top: 20px;">
          Upstairs, the bedrooms are tucked into the eaves. The master has a freestanding bath positioned beneath the skylight — you'll lie there at night and watch the stars through the glass. The children's room has built-in bunks framed in timber, the kind of sleeping nook that makes bedtime an adventure rather than a negotiation. Every room smells faintly of beeswax and old wood.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Room by Room -->
  <section class="section section--stone">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 64px;">
        <h2 data-i18n="grange.rooms.heading">Room by Room</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <div class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card__image">
            <img src="/images/homes/la-grange-living.webp" alt="La Grange master bedroom with freestanding bath beneath the skylight at Moulin à Rêves" />
          </div>
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3 class="card__title" data-i18n="grange.room.master.title">Master Bedroom</h3>
            <p class="card__description" data-i18n="grange.room.master.desc">King bed beneath exposed rafters. Freestanding bath under the skylight. En-suite with walk-in shower and double vanity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card__image">
            <img src="/images/homes/la-grange-living.webp" alt="La Grange garden room with queen bed facing the pear tree at Moulin à Rêves, Barbizon" />
          </div>
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3 class="card__title" data-i18n="grange.room.garden.title">Garden Room</h3>
            <p class="card__description" data-i18n="grange.room.garden.desc">Queen bed facing the pear tree. Warm oak floors, linen curtains, and a writing desk by the window.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card__image">
            <img src="/images/homes/la-grange-living.webp" alt="La Grange children's bunk room with timber-framed beds at Moulin à Rêves" />
          </div>
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3 class="card__title" data-i18n="grange.room.bunk.title">The Bunk Room</h3>
            <p class="card__description" data-i18n="grange.room.bunk.desc">Four built-in bunks framed in reclaimed timber. Reading lights, privacy curtains, and a small porthole window. Children love it here.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card__image">
            <img src="/images/homes/la-grange-living.webp" alt="La Grange open kitchen with reclaimed oak worktops and stoneware at Moulin à Rêves" />
          </div>
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3 class="card__title" data-i18n="grange.room.kitchen.title">Open Kitchen</h3>
            <p class="card__description" data-i18n="grange.room.kitchen.desc">Six-burner range, reclaimed oak worktops, open shelving with hand-thrown stoneware. Dishwasher, double sink, and room to cook together.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card__image">
            <img src="/images/homes/la-grange-living.webp" alt="La Grange five-metre ceiling living space with wood-burning stove at Moulin à Rêves" />
          </div>
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3 class="card__title" data-i18n="grange.room.living.title">Living Space</h3>
            <p class="card__description" data-i18n="grange.room.living.desc">Five-metre ceilings, deep linen sofas, wood-burning stove. The kind of room where conversation happens naturally.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card__image">
            <img src="/images/bridge-garden.webp" alt="La Grange garden terrace with folding doors open to herb garden at Moulin à Rêves" />
          </div>
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3 class="card__title" data-i18n="grange.room.terrace.title">Garden & Terrace</h3>
            <p class="card__description" data-i18n="grange.room.terrace.desc">Folding doors open the kitchen to a stone terrace. Herb garden, wildflowers, the old pear tree, and a table for ten beneath the stars.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Amenities -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container fade-in">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
        <h2 data-i18n="grange.amenities.heading">Amenities</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="amenities">
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.livingspace140">140 m&sup2; living space</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.sleeps6">Sleeps 6</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.wifi">High-speed WiFi</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2z"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.woodstove">Wood-burning stove</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"></path><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.nespresso">Nespresso machine</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.dishwasher">Dishwasher</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 3v18"></path><path d="M5 8l7-5 7 5"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.washerdryer">Washer & dryer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.freestandingbath">Freestanding bath</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.gardenterrace">Garden terrace</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"></path><line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"></line></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.frenchlinens">French linens</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 3h18v18H3z"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.parking">Private parking</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.directgarden">Direct garden access</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.pool">Indoor pool & hot tub</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"></path><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.gym">Gym with stone walls</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.screening">Screening room</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.barn">Covered barn with ping pong & fireplace</span>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
          <span data-i18n="amenity.gazebo">Gazebo dining area</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Location -->
  <section class="section section--stone">
    <div class="container--narrow fade-in text-center">
      <h2 data-i18n="grange.neighbours.heading">Your Neighbours</h2>
      <p data-i18n="grange.neighbours.text" style="margin-top: 24px;">
        La Grange opens directly onto the shared gardens of Moulin a Reves, at the edge of Fontainebleau Forest. Walk ten minutes through the trees and you'll reach the sandstone boulders the local climbers love. Drive ten minutes the other way and you're in Barbizon, ordering a tartine at a sidewalk table. The Chateau de Fontainebleau is twenty minutes. Paris, an hour.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section text-center">
    <div class="container fade-in">
      <h2 data-i18n="grange.cta.heading">Interested in La Grange?</h2>
      <p data-i18n="grange.cta.text" style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
        Tell us your dates and we'll put together everything you need. Pricing is available on inquiry.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary" data-i18n="grange.cta.button">Inquire About Dates</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cross Links -->
  <section class="section section--stone">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
        <h2 data-i18n="grange.otherhomes.heading">The Other Maisons</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--2">
        <a href="/homes/le-moulin/" class="card fade-in" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="card__image">
            <img src="/images/homes/le-moulin-hero.webp" alt="Le Moulin stone mill house with blue shutters at Moulin à Rêves, Barbizon" />
          </div>
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3 class="card__title">Le Moulin</h3>
            <p class="card__description" data-i18n="grange.cross.moulin.desc">The heart of the compound. A stone mill house where thick walls keep summer cool and the millstream runs just outside.</p>
            <span class="link-arrow" data-i18n="grange.cross.moulin.link" style="margin-top: 12px;">Discover Le Moulin</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/homes/le-jardin/" class="card fade-in" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="card__image">
            <img src="/images/homes/le-jardin-hero.webp" alt="Le Jardin garden cottage wrapped in wisteria at Moulin à Rêves, Barbizon" />
          </div>
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3 class="card__title">Le Jardin</h3>
            <p class="card__description" data-i18n="grange.cross.jardin.desc">The quietest of the three. A garden cottage wrapped in wisteria, with a terrace made for long afternoons.</p>
            <span class="link-arrow" data-i18n="grange.cross.jardin.link" style="margin-top: 12px;">Discover Le Jardin</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 48px;">
        <a href="/the-compound/" class="link-arrow" data-i18n="grange.rentall">Rent All Three Maisons</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
